# Changelog
All notable changes to the skin3d library will be documented in this file.

## [Unreleased]

### Added
- New `Render.ts` class replacing the previous `skin3d.ts` - Core rendering engine for 3D player models using Three.js
- New modular structure with separate `index.ts` entry point for cleaner exports
- Refactored module exports: `Model.ts`, `Render.ts`, `Animation.ts`, `Nametag.ts`

### Changed
- Refactored library structure from monolithic entry point to modular component exports
- Updated file naming convention (capitalized: `Animation.ts`, `Model.ts`, `Nametag.ts`, `Render.ts`)
- Modified project dependencies in `package.json` to support new architecture

### Removed
- Legacy `skin3d.ts` entry point (functionality moved to `Render.ts`)
- Legacy `view.ts` file
- Removed `demo/` folder (no longer part of main library distribution)
- Removed `docs/` static folder (now generated dynamically)

---

## [0.1.0] - 2025-12-31

### Added
- Documentation site with TypeDoc-generated API reference
- HTML, CSS, JS, and SVG assets for documentation
- Build script integration (`copy-docs.js`) to generate and copy documentation to static folder
- Documentation pages including class hierarchy, interfaces, and modules

### Fixed
- Corrected background image path in `app.css`

### Changed
- Refactored documentation loading from fetching/processing HTML to direct redirect to static files
- Simplified documentation route handling
- Removed complex loading logic and error handling

---

## [0.0.10] - Previous Release

---

## Library Information

**Version**: 0.1.0  
**Name**: skin3d  
**Description**: A fast, customizable Minecraft skin viewer powered by Three.js. Easily render and preview Minecraft skins in 3D for your projects.  
**License**: MIT  
**Author**: Cosmic-fi (https://github.com/cosmic-fi)  
**Repository**: https://github.com/cosmic-fi/skin3d

### Main Entry Point
- `libs/skin3d.js` (built from TypeScript sources)

### Core Modules
- **Render.ts**: Main rendering engine for 3D player models using Three.js
- **Model.ts**: 3D model handling and management
- **Animation.ts**: Animation system for player movements
- **Nametag.ts**: Nametag rendering and display
- **index.ts**: Main export point for all public APIs

### Key Dependencies
- **three**: 3D graphics library
- **skinview-utils**: Minecraft skin utilities and texture handling

### Build Scripts
- `npm run build`: Complete build (modules, bundles, and preview)
- `npm run build:modules`: Compile TypeScript to JavaScript
- `npm run build:bundles`: Create browser bundles with Rollup
- `npm run build:docs`: Generate TypeDoc documentation
- `npm run dev:watch:modules`: Watch mode for module compilation
- `npm run dev:watch:bundles`: Watch mode for bundle creation
- `npm run format`: Format code with Prettier
- `npm run test:lint`: Run ESLint
